data.description:
BANYAN SPRINGS/Gated - 55+ Active Community - Garage 1st floor Villa - Beautifully landscaped. If you are looking for added extras and peace of mind this house has it! NEW Hurricane Impact windows & garage door! Glassed in lanai with A/C. 6.7 KW solar panels on roof. Only home in Banyan Springs with Solar. Whole house surge protection for sewer and water lines. Washer/dryer in unit.3 Bedroom 2 full bathrooms. Some kitchen appliances are newer. Convection oven 2020.  A/C - 2015, Hot water tank is electric and is 2020. Extra enclosed area off of the kitchen for added storage and dinning. Electric box replaced in 2018. Updated owners suite bathroom. With larger shower and no tub. Have you always wanted orchids. Now you can place them in your private enclosed lanai off of the 2nd bathroom. Roof is less than 10 years old! Bedrooms are carpeted. Tile floor everywhere else. Lots of clubs, activities and theater nights. Clubhouse with restaurant.Exercise Room, hair & nail salon, entertainment, numerous clubs, card rooms, billiards, art club, pickle ball court, shuffleboard, bocce ball, library, bike, walk or jog on private sidewalks & more! Conveniently located to 95 and the turnpike
Great location. Close to grocery stores, malls, restaurants, beaches and so much more! Near 195 and the turnpike. All Sizes and Measurements are approximate, not verified and not guaranteed!
